main event: Two civilians reported sighting a flying object near Cedar Hill, Texas on the night of 22-23 August 1952.
interesting points: The sighting was reported by two presumed fly fishermen in the area., One of the witnesses remains unidentified., The object was sighted west of Dallas at approximately five to seven angles., No further investigation was conducted to gather more information., A written report was expected to follow the sighting, dated 4 August 1952.
